{"tid":1854460,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"同啲護士fd傾過，發現話被道德綁架唔罷嗰班其實視野唔夠闊","createTime":"2020-01-31T13:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T13:41:56.000Z","uid":56146,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed216bf7bfc604b1bd45f5ff11f33fd440594ec8","tid":1854460,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"講緊嗰班想罷又話自己被道德綁架嗰班醫護猶豫不決，其實著眼只有自己病房。但再諗深一層，今次行動一嚟為前線隔離病房前線出聲，二嚟同政府講防護不足會連累上千名職員，三嚟唔封關病源體源源不絕，只會引發社區爆發。當中會害到嘅人一定比你哋病房四五十個多。<br />\n前線人手不足，搵返班冷氣admin上返前線，重拾昔日動力，體驗吓人手不足嘅問題都係一個好處"},{"pid":"c7f620e6a7da6e6767c9911312266c7b7382ca78","tid":1854460,"uid":126621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"搵黑警做<br />\n人工咁高，包架"},{"pid":"2fe512013ba3aa243d6e7d6ba26c6cad096effea","tid":1854460,"uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"1.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫護界資源比狗隊少</span></strong><br />\nblue object <span style=\"color: red;\">24,110元 至 38,580元 </span><br />\nwhite object <span style=\"color: gold;\">45,305元 至 84,250元</span> <br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=b852177c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span>"},{"pid":"0fd7a8bfcddf886a64a33d9c3c5f6ad504beb5ab","tid":1854460,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"Exactly<br />\n幫緊acute果班發聲"},{"pid":"5108c1855af671da9059bbd484ec0a80f0daddf6","tid":1854460,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"exactly"},{"pid":"82af6972fbb857d405a1ac9268434982e5187b99","tid":1854460,"uid":270905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"道德綁架完，醫護死撚哂到時就真係冇人救啦"},{"pid":"df46a6dd0fb6ca4d6cec5ee7570f915944d2b8e3","tid":1854460,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:25:25.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\nnow or never<br />\n生死存亡<br />\n政府唔做<br />\n我地自己做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e5053f3222c58e687410e7732669965479a639","tid":1854460,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nusoOoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnusoOoa.jpg&h=d5f12261&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"790264733a42d84bc08b9c6b309c72fcccbd7952","tid":1854460,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"藍屍視野一向短淺同只睇個人利益"},{"pid":"39544cc60ff0290eec5063293e280c88fe7a5396","tid":1854460,"uid":